snippet.textDisplay:
"ke muhammar sy wafa tuny to hm tery hein
yae jahan cheez hy kya loh o qalam b tery hein"
For those who don't understand, this verse is very deep. "Loh o Qalam" means pen and ink, Iqbal says if you stay loyal to Muhammad (PBUH), you will be given the ink and pen to write your own destiny which normally God does for you.

پھر ان شاہيں بچوں کو بال و پر دے 
خدايا! آرزو ميري يہي ہے 
مرا نور بصيرت عام کر دے

Give wings to these eaglets again,
This, dear Lord, is my only wish—
That my insights should be shared by all!
